    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet149"/>, quoted according to
                    the catalogue description in <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><citedRange unit="page">579</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab> 
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፱፡
                        <sic>ለሚ<surplus>ለሚ</surplus>ያዘያ፡</sic> ዘደረሰ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኤጲፋንዮስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ቆጵሮስ፡ ካልእ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                        ወመጽአ፡ መልአከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <expan><abbr>ቅዱ</abbr><ex>ስ፡</ex></expan> ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ገብርኤል፡ 
                        እምሰማይ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab>
                        ወቀንዑ፡ ለገቢረ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ወቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ይትራድኦሙ፡
                        በኵሉ፡ መዋዕል፨ ወከመዝ፡ ኮነ፡ ግብሩ፡ ለእዉር፡ ወልደ፡ አብራሲት፡ መሠርይ፨ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
